  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/44ea5017dbbe8e7c407c13c06f0f319a.poster.avif?t=1701968039\" width=506 height=86 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/44ea5017dbbe8e7c407c13c06f0f319a.webm?t=1701968039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/44ea5017dbbe8e7c407c13c06f0f319a.mp4?t=1701968039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Welcome to Courier Chief Tycoon !</strong><br><br>Courier Chief Tycoon is a game that lets you build and operate your own package delivery network. It offers you all the mechanics you need to grow your business.<br><br>So what awaits you;<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/8dd65b6278eed22fccf3c880a57687cd.avif?t=1701968039\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>-Couriers that you can assign in your company,<br>-Different features from each other.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/7a018548f971eb4ad2898c28e4156743.avif?t=1701968039\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>-Panels where you can check your stock status,<br>-Panels that you can order according to your needs.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/1079a8eedc97875da1a1caad9f7921ba.avif?t=1701968039\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>-Qualified software that you can purchase from your internet network,<br>Each software has its own features.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/6ce9b26aa563e43c2919bd0fa5676bc5.avif?t=1701968039\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>-The games on the site that you can use to add a new one to your entertainment,<br>-Some games can earn you balance.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/173d101263d8ad916933f32f45806b66.avif?t=1701968039\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>-Crypto panels that you can navigate when you activate the secure network access,<br>-You can provide additional income to your company and accelerate your development.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/6344f7566e5bf6c254e97a937f7307b5.avif?t=1701968039\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>-Engine gallery where you can give your employees an advantage with different engines,<br>-Interactions where you can strengthen the engines you have.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/89cc417691741c6a1ddf8e7b472b40bc.avif?t=1701968039\" width=620 height=346 /></span><br><br><strong>-Notification panels where you can check your customers' comments,<br>-Control panels where you can deal with your customers' orders.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/44ea5017dbbe8e7c407c13c06f0f319a.poster.avif?t=1701968039\" width=506 height=86 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/44ea5017dbbe8e7c407c13c06f0f319a.webm?t=1701968039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225220/extras/44ea5017dbbe8e7c407c13c06f0f319a.mp4?t=1701968039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
